# Question 01

## Data science everywhere!
Every time you shop online, scroll through social media, or receive a fraud alert on your credit card, data science is working behind the scenes. Data science is becoming increasingly important in today's world, helping businesses, governments, and individuals make sense of complex information.

How does data science create value in our daily lives?

- [ ] `Data science is mainly about storing and collecting large amounts of data.`
- [x] `Data science helps analyze patterns, make predictions, and improve decision-making.`
- [ ] `Data science ensures that businesses will never face problems again.`
- [ ] `Data science can replace human employees in all decision-making roles.`
